<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Presupuesto</title>
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 15mm;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24pt;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 9pt;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-top: 3px;
        }
        
        .info-section {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 50%;
            vertical-align: top;
            padding: 10px 15px;
        }
        
        .info-box:first-child {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .info-box h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 11pt;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .info-box p {
            margin: 3px 0;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }
        
        .document-info {
            text-align: right;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        
        .document-info p {
            margin: 2px 0;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }
        
        .document-info strong {
            color: #667eea;
        }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        thead {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        th {
            padding: 10px 8px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 9pt;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        th.right {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        td {
            padding: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }
        
        td.right {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        tbody tr:hover {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .totals-section {
            margin-top: 10px;
            float: right;
            width: 280px;
        }
        
        .totals-row {
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 6px 0;
        }
        
        .totals-label {
            display: table-cell;
            text-align: right;
            padding-right: 15px;
            font-size: 9pt;
        }
        
        .totals-value {
            display: table-cell;
            text-align: right;
            width: 100px;
            font-size: 9pt;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .total-final {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .total-final .totals-label,
        .total-final .totals-value {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .footer-note {
            clear: both;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        
        .footer-note p {
            margin: 3px 0;
        }
        
        .footer-note strong {
            color: #495057;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>PRESUPUESTO</h1>
        <p>Entre Brochas - Pinturas Profesionales</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="document-info">
        <p><strong>Nº Presupuesto:</strong> {{ presupuesto_numero }}</p>
        <p><strong>Fecha:</strong> {{ fecha }}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="info-section">
        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Datos de la Empresa</h3>
            <p><strong>Entre Brochas S.L.</strong></p>
            <p>CIF: B12345678</p>
            <p>Calle del Pintor 23, 28015 Madrid</p>
            <p>Tel: +34 910 123 456</p>
            <p>presupuestos@entrebrochas.es</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Datos del Cliente</h3>
            <p><strong>{{ cliente_nombre }}</strong></p>
            <p>NIF: {{ cliente_nif }}</p>
            <p>{{ cliente_direccion }}</p>
            <p>{{ cliente_email }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Descripción</th>
                <th class="right">Cantidad</th>
                <th class="right">Precio Unit.</th>
                <th class="right">Importe</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {% for item in items %}
            <tr>
                <td>{{ item.concepto }}</td>
                <td class="right">{{ item.cantidad }}</td>
                <td class="right">{{ item.precio_unitario }}</td>
                <td class="right">{{ item.importe }}</td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
    </table>
    
    <div class="totals-section">
        <div class="totals-row">
            <div class="totals-label">Base Imponible:</div>
            <div class="totals-value">{{ base_imponible }} €</div>
        </div>
        <div class="totals-row">
            <div class="totals-label">IVA (21%):</div>
            <div class="totals-value">{{ iva }} €</div>
        </div>
        <div class="totals-row total-final">
            <div class="totals-label">TOTAL:</div>
            <div class="totals-value">{{ total }} €</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer-note">
        <p><strong>Validez:</strong> 30 días | <strong>Pago:</strong> 50% inicio, 50% finalización</p>
        <p>Trabajos adicionales no incluidos se facturarán aparte. Gracias por su confianza.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>